title: [1963] Various Jazz Artists - Americans In Europe (320kbps)
description:
Rare Impulse recording of American Jazz Artists living in Europe giving a Jazz concert. Recorded January 3, 1963 in Koblenz, Germany. Includes artists such as Kenny Clarke, Lou Bennett, Bud Powell, Don Byas, Jimmy Woode, Idress Sulieman, Jimmy Gourley, Joe Harris, Bill Smith, Herb Geller, & Bob Carter. Quality is 320kbps.
